snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - A.K.I. Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A maniacal poison aficionado, A.K.I. can’t wait to sink her nails into her opponents as the second character from Year 1. 

Owners of the Deluxe and Ultimate Edition or the Year 1 Character Pass and Ultimate Pass of Street Fighter 6 will obtain A.K.I. when she releases in Autumn 2023.

https://streetfighter.com/6/

#StreetFighter6 #Capcom #AKI
